  "appearance": {
    "en": "Hydralazine Hydrochloride occurs as a white crystalline powder. It is odorless, and has a bitter taste. It is soluble in water, slightly soluble in ethanol (95), and practically insoluble in diethyl ether. Melting point: about 2759C (with decomposition)."
  },
